  "2372450": {
    "name": "Rootin' Tootin' Lootin' & Shootin'",
    "steam_appid": 2372450,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372450/extras/7c55f7cf97d5faa0b691df5037e8e625.avif?t=1757848863\" width=616 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan out your turns to skilfully weave between bullets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress deeper, your enemies will have deadlier and more dastardly bullet patterns, so don’t get overwhelmed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372450/extras/188d78dcd60ee5d9237c5f437e100b76.avif?t=1757848863\" width=616 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every single weapon does something unique – Bat bullets back with a Baseball Bat, freeze enemies with an Ice Blast or even jump over bullets with a Feather!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You never know what you’re gonna get when you smash open a weapon crate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372450/extras/6d0665dae0d497d0735f529ab4564cf8.avif?t=1757848863\" width=616 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrades change the way you play – Hover over bottomless pits, turn your weapons into automatic turrets or even remote control your bullets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can only hold so many upgrades – choose wisely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372450/extras/c70f95b5dbcd53d720fb987e11678b30.avif?t=1757848863\" width=616 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With snappy gameplay and no waiting for enemy turns, you can blast through the game at whatever pace you like – but don’t forget to slow down if you need to!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372450/extras/4297342027adf55c9b7b32d66e2ca2de.avif?t=1757848863\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep killing enemies to keep up your combo and get more coins! Each turn wasted will tick down the timer, so keep the pressure on your foes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
